lead_paragraph: Rookie Aledmys Diaz had his first five-hit game, Jedd Gyorko and Jeremy Hazelbaker hit three-run homers and the St. Louis Cardinals beat the San Diego Padres 11-2 on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: Gyorko, Hazelbaker Hit 3-Run Homers in Cardinals' 11-2 Win
